		p	2		y	
		p	3		z	
	m	(IIII)Z	m_44543878	hasSignal	
		c	Returns whether the block at the given position is emitting a redstone signal in the given direction.\nThis roughly equates to what is colloquially known as 'soft' or 'weak' power.\n\n<p>\nNOTE: directions in redstone signal related methods are backwards, so this method\nchecks for the signal emitted in the direction <i>opposite</i> of the one given.	
		p	1		x	
		p	2		y	
		p	3		z	
		p	4		dir	
